POST CABINET MEDIA BRIEFING 3 September 2014The Minister in The Presidency responsible for Planning, Monitoring and Evaluation, Mr Jeff Radebe, will address members of the media on the outcomes of the Cabinet meeting held in Cape Town today. He will be joined by both the Minister and Deputy Minister for Public Works, Messrs Thulas Nxesi and Jeremy Cronin.Members of the media are invited to the media briefing as follows:Date: Thursday, 04 September 2014 Time: 10h00 Venue: Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape TownNB: There will be a video-link to GCIS Head Office, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard Street, Hatfield, PTARSVP:Pheliswa Sebati (Pretoria) Cell: 082 413 4609 E-mail: pheliswa@gcis.gov.zaMzimasi Ngqelu (Cape Town) Cell: 076 904 3557 E-mail: Mzi@gcis.gov.zaEnquiries: Phumla Williams Cell: 083 501 0139Issued by: Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)